178
00:24:55,220 --> 00:24:55,810
Fiancee...!

179
00:25:00,760 --> 00:25:02,690
I don't like you being friends
with Akash at all

180
00:25:04,060 --> 00:25:07,830
His behaviour the other night...
You know how embarrassed I was?

181
00:25:09,300 --> 00:25:10,330
Let him do what he wants.

182
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:11,730
Just keep away from him

183
