186
00:25:20,910 --> 00:25:24,680
Just decide, Sameer. You can
either be with Akash or me!

187
00:25:31,490 --> 00:25:32,050
I am thinking...

188
00:25:32,890 --> 00:25:35,550
You need time to think
if you want to be with me!

189
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,960
Okay. So you want some time?

190
00:25:41,270 --> 00:25:41,730
No!

191
00:25:44,870 --> 00:25:47,600
I'm going out with friends.
I'll be back by 2.00

192
00:25:48,440 --> 00:25:52,840
If I don't hear from you before that,
I'll know what your answer is

193
00:25:57,620 --> 00:25:59,780
Don't you think you are
over-reacting?

194
00:26:02,290 --> 00:26:02,780
No

195
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:09,380
You've never seen me over-react.
If I do... then God help you!!

196
00:26:31,980 --> 00:26:32,540
What are you doing!

197
