692
01:24:50,530 --> 01:24:51,360
Sameer, are you coming?

693
01:25:40,560 --> 01:25:41,820
I still remember that night

694
01:25:49,970 --> 01:25:52,270
I never thought things would go
that far

695
01:25:58,680 --> 01:25:59,770
I couldn't sleep all night

696
01:26:01,350 --> 01:26:02,840
I went and met Akash
the next morning

697
