Have you been to Sydney before?

744
01:31:11,820 --> 01:31:13,380
Do you always ask so many
questions?

745
01:31:13,930 --> 01:31:16,220
Yes. Have you been to Sydney
before?

746
01:31:17,030 --> 01:31:17,500
Yes

747
