Okay but I will have to ask
my uncle

753
01:31:40,790 --> 01:31:42,380
But he won't refuse.

754
01:31:43,020 --> 01:31:43,490
Why?

755
01:31:44,260 --> 01:31:45,520
Because I have bought him a gift!

756
01:32:18,290 --> 01:32:20,450
